replies.body:
{{champion:16}} 
She is now a stupid healbot. She has pretty good AP rating on heal and ult, but you can't go ap because then you just die without helping your team. Q range was nerfed, so you don't have enough safe range to regen your hp, and regeneration is plain shit, and ap ratio is worthless. Going ap is just a disadvantage right now instead of being viable strategy.

P.S. Also, i miss giving mana to people :(
